app_detail:
aa is the "hello world" app for Android Phones & Tablets. The simplest but most addictive game in the Android Play Store.

i.e. aa is like snake on an old brick phone, it's fundamental.

Handmade in Australia,
General Adaptive



If it's not published by General Adaptive Apps Pty Ltd - it's not the authentic and original aa. Don't be fooled by clones.
aa는 Android 휴대 전화 및 태블릿 용 "안녕하세요 세상"앱입니다. Android Play 스토어에서 가장 단순하지만 가장 중독성있는 게임입니다.

즉 aa는 오래된 벽돌 전화의 뱀과 같아서 근본적입니다.
